text: The 'Human' Factor is a 1975 British Italian thriller movie directed by Edward Dmytryk and starring George Kennedy, John Mills, Raf Vallone, Rita Tushingham, Haydee Politoff, Danny Huston, Jan Englund. It was distributed by Bryanston Distribution. ==Other websites== * Category:1975 thriller movies Category:British thriller movies Category:Italian thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Edward Dmytryk Category:Vigilante movies Category:Movies set in Italy Category:Movies set in Naples Category:Movies about the Central Intelligence Agency
